界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
“ 据楚天都市报微信公号消息，彭银华原本打算正月初八举办婚礼，但因为疫情发展，彭银华决定坚守在一线。
"According to the official letter of the Chu Tian Metropolis Daily, Peng Yinhua had planned to hold the wedding on January 8, but due to the epidemic situation, Peng Yinhua decided to stay on the front line.
而婚礼的请柬，还放在办公桌抽屉里，没来得及分发。
The wedding invitation was still in the desk drawer before it could be handed out.
”2020年2月20日晚，武汉市江夏区第一人民医院/协和江南医院发布公告称，该院呼吸与危重症医学科医生彭银华，在抗击疫情一线不幸感染新冠肺炎，于2020年2月20日21时50分在武汉市金银潭医院去世。
On the night of February 20, 2020, Peng Yinhua, the hospital's respiratory and critically ill physician, died on February 20, 2020 at 2150 hours at the Jianghe Hospital in Wuhan, the city's No. 1 People's Hospital / Concorde Jiangnan Hospital said.
据公告内容，彭银华在抗击疫情一线不幸感染新冠肺炎，于1月25日入住江夏区第一人民医院，医院随即全力救治；1月30日病情加重，医院紧急将其送往武汉市金银潭医院治疗。
According to the announcement, Peng Yinhua was admitted to the First People's Hospital of Jiangxia District on January 25 to fight the epidemic. He was admitted to the First People's Hospital in Jiangxia.
因病情恶化，经抢救无效，于2月20日21时50分在武汉市金银潭医院去世。
Due to the deterioration of his condition, he died at 21: 50 a.m. on 20 February at the Gold and Silver Pool Hospital in Wuhan.
据楚天都市报微信公号消息，彭银华原本打算正月初八举办婚礼，但因为疫情发展，彭银华决定坚守在一线。
According to the official letter of the Chu Tian Metropolis Daily, Peng Yinhua had planned to hold the wedding on January 8th, but due to the epidemic situation, Peng Yinhua decided to stay on the front line.
而婚礼的请柬，还放在办公桌抽屉里，没来得及分发。
The wedding invitation was still in the desk drawer before it could be handed out.
据报道，从第一例新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎患者确诊，到隔离病区组建，作为江夏区第一人民医院一名呼吸内科医生，彭银华坚守在隔离病区抗击疫情“白班加夜班”轮班倒，虽然陆续有更多医生请战加入进来，压力得到些许缓解，但随着疫情的发展，彭银华选择了坚守。
As a respiratory physician at the First People's Hospital in Jiangxia District, Peng Yinhua stuck in the quarantined area to fight the epidemic on a shift of "day shift plus night shift." But as the outbreak progressed, Peng Yinhua chose to stick to it.
据公告显示，1月25日（正月初一），彭银华入住江夏区第一人民医院，到2月20日（正月二十七），彭银华在医院里救治了27天。
According to the announcement, January 25 (the first day of the first month), Peng Yinhua checked into the Jiangxia District First People's Hospital, February 20 (27), Peng Yinhua in the hospital for 27 days.
微博认证为武汉市金银潭医院护士的网友“吃胖的瘦子_ ”发文悼念道：“以为你输过血浆后并且后好转，你才29岁，很遗憾用这种方式认识你，彭医生一路走好。
"I thought you were 29 years old after you lost your plasma," mourned Wei Bo, a netizen who certified as a nurse at Wuhan Gold and Silver Pool Hospital. "I'm sorry to have met you this way, Dr. Peng said
”据不完全统计，彭银华之前，已有梁武东、李文亮、林正斌、柳帆、刘智明等多位武汉医护人员在疫情中去世。
According to incomplete statistics, Mr. Pang had already died of the epidemic in Wuhan, including Liang Wudong, Li Wenliang, Lin Zhengbin, Liufan and Liu Zhiming.
